sinks.name: Sink1
sinks.script:
sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet',
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> Sink1

typeProperties.script:
section Section1;
shared Parquet2 = let
  AdfDoc = AzureStorage.DataLakeContents("https://ophackmdwteam10stgacc.dfs.core.windows.net/cosmosdbmovies/Movies"),
  Parquet = Parquet.Document(AdfDoc)
in
  Parquet;
shared UserQuery = let
  Source = Parquet2,
  #"Filtered rows" = Table.SelectRows(Source, each [id] <> null and [id] <> "")
in
  #"Filtered rows";
